Text:
I was really hoping to have this book; however, the quality is (sadly) horrible.  It skips like a scratched CD the entire time.  I had to delete the torrent just because of that.

Hate to give bad credit, but I can't recommend this torrent to anyone.  If you could get another copy up and running, that'd be awesome.

Thanks anyway for the effort.

(if it's not the same for anyone else, that'd be great to know)

@ fakeplastictrousers2 : can you please post epub or pdf if u have it!
thanks!
